<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11287</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，凯蒂和乔伊骑着自行车去布恩小学。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>21038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们都很兴奋。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>21038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂等不及每个人都看到她的新刘海。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊想把小鸡的事告诉大家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>33786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“卢克在那儿！”乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>33786</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她朝一个穿着T恤的男孩挥了挥手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>T恤上写着“我挖蚯蚓”。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克是凯蒂和乔伊的表弟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“乔伊。”凯蒂说，“你为什么不等到希金斯老师上科学课呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49037</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53206</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，告诉大家关于小鸡的事。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57204</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>学习动物也是科学的一部分。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57204</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59268</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊犹豫了一下。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59268</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，如果你这么认为的话。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66667</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想我可以等到上科学课。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70170</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但凯蒂迫不及待地想分享她的新闻。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70170</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>72890</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嘿，卢克！我剪了个刘海！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>72890</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，没人会把我和乔伊搞混了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80286</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。这很好。”卢克回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80286</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你的诱饵生意怎么样？”凯蒂问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87537</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>卢克抓蚯蚓卖给加油站的渔民。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87537</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90284</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“非常好。”卢克说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“周六，我卖了八杯蚯蚓，每杯一美元。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94035</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98785</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>等到夏天，我想我的蚯蚓不够卖了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98785</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>102285</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“劳拉来了！”乔伊喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>102285</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105288</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>劳拉·莱曼也在三年级。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105288</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108742</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“有什么新闻？”劳拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108742</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我剪了个刘海。”凯蒂脱口而出。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我有件令人兴奋的事儿要告诉大家。”乔伊低声对劳拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118968</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121720</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但我还不能说。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126222</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奥尔森校长站在学校正门前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126222</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，双胞胎。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132469</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，卢克，劳拉。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136219</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“早上好，奥尔森校长。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“从现在起，记住凯蒂就是那个有刘海的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141220</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好，谢谢你告诉我。”奥尔森校长回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>150684</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希金斯老师在三年级教室门口等着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>150684</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你好，卢克。你好，劳拉，”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们好，双胞胎。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>160185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“凯蒂在这儿。”凯蒂说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>160185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162438</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我就是那个有刘海的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162438</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167188</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她想：“今天会是个好日子。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天的第一项活动是数学练习题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171685</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>174937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂错了三道除法题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>174937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>177439</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊算出了所有问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>177439</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183937</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在拼写课上，凯蒂把“cheese”中的S错拼成了Z。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乔伊拼对了每个单词。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191539</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了艺术课的时候，凯蒂的泥马站不起来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191539</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但乔伊的泥羊看起来很完美。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195054</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201059</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天这么好的一天，我是怎么了？”凯蒂想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>203554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她觉得事情会变得更糟。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>203554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text> 接下来是科学课，这意味着乔伊很快就会引起大家的注意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>209553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，卢克给班上的同学们看他挖的一条吓人的蚯蚓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218302</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>它有23厘米长！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>221553</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>接下来，乔伊举起手来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>221553</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226053</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂突然从座位上站了起来。“听我说！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希金斯老师和全班同学看着凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230052</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234055</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要养小鸡了。”凯蒂说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237304</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她听到乔伊的叹气声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>242554</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是个特大新闻。”希金斯老师说，“它们会多大？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>242554</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯，它们真的很小。”凯蒂很快地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247802</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一天。”乔伊回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>253388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>希金斯老师转向乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>253388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258386</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦。”他说。然后，他回头看着凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要养多少只小鸡？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260388</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>265639</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也许三只吧。”凯蒂回答。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>66</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>265639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>270635</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她看着乔伊，乔伊眯起眼睛看着凯蒂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>67</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>270635</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“六只。”乔伊纠正了她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>68</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273385</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277136</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小鸡吃什么？”希金斯老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>69</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277136</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你要养只公鸡吗？”卢克问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>70</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它们会想它们的妈妈吗？”劳拉问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>71</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285636</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂为自己多嘴而感到很抱歉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>72</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>291638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她毁了乔伊的一切。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>73</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>291638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296888</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在，她连一个问题也答不上来。她看着乔伊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>74</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296888</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>299885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”乔伊接过话题说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>75</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>299885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>302886</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首先，它们会有特别的食物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>76</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>302886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>305640</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她拿出她的小鸡目录。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>77</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>305640</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>309140</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都聚在乔伊的书桌旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>78</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>309140</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313637</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我们挑选出来的小鸡。”她自豪地解释说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>79</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>319636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>凯蒂静静地坐在自己的书桌旁听着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>